WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.066 --> 00:00:02.900
Lin Chenxi, you are so brave

2
00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:06.500
How dare you touch my daughter's brother?

3
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:07.733
Pardon me?

4
00:00:07.733 --> 00:00:09.100
I don't understand.

5
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:11.366
A light car accident is planned by you

6
00:00:11.366 --> 00:00:12.566
She's my daughter.

7
00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:14.233
He is my own daughter

8
00:00:14.533 --> 00:00:17.200
Lin Chenxi, how do you chase him away?

9
00:00:24.133 --> 00:00:25.833
I didn't know he was your daughter

10
00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:27.900
I didn't even know he was going to be in a car accident

11
00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:31.366
I just wanted to take him to you that day

12
00:00:31.366 --> 00:00:33.666
His car accident was an accident

13
00:00:33.666 --> 00:00:36.766
Accident, my people have already checked it out.

14
00:00:36.766 --> 00:00:38.833
You found the trick driver

15
00:00:40.766 --> 00:00:42.200
Prairie brother

16
00:00:42.300 --> 00:00:45.766
Please, I'm just obsessed

17
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:48.300
I'm afraid you'll abandon me for money

18
00:00:48.733 --> 00:00:51.866
I only have a short life, you know

19
00:00:51.866 --> 00:00:53.900
I just want to be with you

20
00:00:53.900 --> 00:00:54.900
Random brother

21
00:00:54.966 --> 00:00:57.366
You see for the sake of me only having one life

22
00:00:57.400 --> 00:00:59.500
But spare me this time

